# ============================================================
# CRAMWIZ ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
# Add these in Vercel → Settings → Environment Variables
# NEVER commit real values to Git
# ============================================================

# FREE Gemini API Key
# Get yours free at: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
